                "title": "轰闪落雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷萤</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/ba8a520b631a5349ea54ca1fad2ec264_8644419440078736612.png",
                "id": "talent55280",
                "key": "雾虚之召",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雾虚之召"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>，本角色<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">附着雷元素</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷萤护罩</span>并准备技能<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">霆电迸发</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/58e7aa03ca09a144cdac07649148383f_1836787288124762040.png",
                "id": "talent60618",
                "key": "霆雷之护",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "霆雷之护"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超载</span>：本伤害<span>+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span><span>]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_704508979076666259.png",
                "id": "talent55758",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：3</span><br><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">敌方累计打出3张行动牌后：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>+1。（最多叠加到3）<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">愚人众·雷萤术士受到元素反应伤害后：</span>此牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>-1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_226177063543352414.png",
                "id": "talent55435",
                "key": "雷萤",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/c32e8d1f898b13385973738aba9d5c6a_2077134023659171113.png",
                "title": "雷萤"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">附着雷元素<br></span></strong>不通过伤害附着雷元素时，发生的元素反应会忽略伤害效果：<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载：</span>目标强制切换到下一个角色<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导：</span>没有效果<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电：</span>没有效果<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化：</span>生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷萤护罩<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾<br></span>为我方出战角色提供<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1点护盾</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">创建时：</span>如果我方场上存在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷萤</span>，则额外提供其<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>。（最多额外提供3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span>）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">霆电迸发<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发<br></span>（需准备1个行动轮）<br>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6692676922015699056.png",
